	DefineInfo 0x0009
		Name = "Rocky"
		Description = "If you fall into a ravine, call Lassie. If you need help in Office, call Rocky."
		ExtraData = "Got a question? Put me to work.~~Problem? Relax, I'm on it.~~Don't worry, I'm fully Office-trained.^^Here's your reminder.~~You asked me to remind you about this."
